ALTER PROC [dbo].[ImportDimActors] AS begin
insert into dbo.DimActors
(
	ActorID
	, ActorName
	, ActorGender
)
SELECT * FROM (  
select
	isnull(max(ActorID), lower(newid()))
	, ActorName
	, isnull(max(ActorGender), 'U')
from extern.[catalog]
group by ActorName
) cleaned_table
WHERE cleaned_table.ActorID NOT IN (SELECT ActorID FROM [dbo].[DimActors])
;
END
GO
